STOP SENDING GREAT TRAFFIC INTO THE ABYSS

Bad Landing Pages Steal Your Money

Is great traffic not converting because your landing pages suck?

How bad landing pages steal your money

Your design is working against you

People design their pages and many times the way people look at them is entirely different from what the creator intended. Unfortunately, this makes them underperform and lose conversions left, right, and center.

Your page is too slow

Google punishes you with lower Page Experience Scores when your page is slow. They know that slow pages kill conversions.

Your headlines & content suck

The copy on your website is your silent salesperson. A lifeless salesperson doesn't sell well in person. Same goes for websites. Bad headlines and webpage content also don't sell. Killing your conversions and profits.

Your page isn't relevant to the search query

What do you think would work better? A web page that talks about the query someone has typed into the search engine, or some generic guff that doesn't answer anything specific. Unfortunately, most web pages are generic instead of specific. What's even worse is that Google punishes your Quality Score, which also drives up your click costs.

How Ad Alchemy turns around bad landing pages

It gives you AI based eye tracking data

We give you the functionality of on-demand eye tracking with our AI Attention heatmaps. Developed out of university research, we can show you where people look and where they don't helping you design your pages to convert!

It shows you how to improve the speed

Blazing-fast pages help with both your PPC campaigns as well as your conversions. Ad Alchemy tells you what you need to fix to increase the speed.

It helps you create killer headlines

After years of testing, headlines are the easiest and most important thing you can improve to increase headlines. We help you improve your headlines using best practice with a sprinkle of AI.

Improves your content structure for conversions

High-performing content shares common best practices. The Ad Alchemy Landing Page analysis makes recommendations based on what works in the real world.

Makes your page more relevant with DKI

Our JavaScript, WordPress and Cloudflare dynamic keyword insertion (DKI) landing page solutions help make your landing pages more relevant at scale. You'll be rewarded with better Google Page Experience Scores, Quality Scores, and conversion rates.

Frequently Asked Questions

Have questions? We've answers.

Does Ad Alchemy offer a landing page builder as part of the software?

No, we don't offer any kind of landing page builder. What we do offer is both analysis on how to improve your existing landing pages, plus ways to make your landing pages have dynamic keyword insertion capabilities.

Do you offer a dynamic keyword insertion (DKI) plug-in for Wordpress?

We sure do. This plug-in is included and provided for use while subscribed to the Solo+ and Agency plans.

What's the story with the Cloudflare DKI solution?

If you proxy your website using Cloudflare, we provide the code that allows you to turn on dynamic keyword insertion capabilities for any website (even static websites). It's done at the edge (CDN) so it's super fast as well!

How does the AI Attention Heatmap functionality work?

The AI Attention Heatmaps replicate eye tracking studies with over 90% accuracy (based on university research). This then allows you to see if people are really looking at (and giving their attention) to what you think they are!

Does Ad Alchemy work with other DKI functionality from landing page solutions like Unbounce and Swipe Pages?

It sure does! Provided you can pass values into those pages through the URL, we can make it work.
